1
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,840
Look at the time.

2
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:57,080
Did they cancel the date?

3
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,440
I'm sure he's at home.

4
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,960
If they cancelled their date today,

5
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:04,760
it means our job is done.

6
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:07,520
Sisters united can overcome anything.

7
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,360
Do you remember

8
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,120
their expressions after you said that?

9
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:14,040
It was like a bolt from the blue.

10
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,160
They were dumbfounded on the spot.

11
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,940
There is no disease we can't cure.

12
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,960
Oh my god, no way.

13
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:30,920
Let's go.

14
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,360
I want to leave a good impression.

15
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:40,960
It's okay.

16
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,520
Just wait for me in the park.

17
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,079
I'll be there after I change.

18
00:02:44,079 --> 00:02:45,040
Don't worry.

19
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:47,180
I won't be late for our first date.

20
00:02:58,600 --> 00:02:59,600
What should we do?

21
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,320
Calm down.

22
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:04,740
Looks like all three of our plans failed.

23
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:07,640
Grab the weapons and hit them hard.

24
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:25,520
No.

25
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,770
We can't let things go on like this.

26
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,000
Grab the weapons.

27
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,520
Let's fight.

28
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,260
What are you two doing?

29
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,440
We were about to ask what you two are doing.

30
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,040
Yeah.

31
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,460
What are you doing?

32
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:54,000
Yuanbao, Qingyun.

33
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,520
Gong Yu, what are you doing?

34
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:20,320
I heard you're a good fighter.

35
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,980
I heard you're not bad either.

36
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,930
Mu Qingyun, I know you are the top guy in Zhicheng.

37
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,040
But for me,

38
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,400
I don't like being an underling.

39
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:29,860
I only like being the boss.

40
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:32,720
So give up your position.

41
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,040
Sure.

42
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:39,400
Take it if you can.

43
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:43,120
Alright, let's see how well you can fight.

44
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:50,240
Gong Yu!

45
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:50,800
Qingyun!

46
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,640
What are you doing?

47
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:52,570
What's going on?

48
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:53,690
Grandma!

49
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,040
Grandpa!

50
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,640
Are they classmates?

51
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,560
Apologize.

52
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,560
Come, shake hands.

53
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:20,840
Wenying,

54
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,360
it's you.

55
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,280
It's you.

56
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,280
Yeah,

57
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,280
it's been so many years.

58
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:43,040
To think that my grandpa and Yuanbao's grandma

59
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:45,100
knew each other when they were young.

60
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,640
Yeah.

61
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,280
The thing is,

62
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,840
it seems they're

63
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,480
more than just acquaintances.

64
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,940
You don't know my grandpa.

65
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,440
After he went back that day,

66
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:56,400
he combed his hair, looked in the mirror,

67
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,640
and even dug out old photos.

68
00:05:57,640 --> 00:06:00,720
Do you think it's possible

69
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:03,400
between my grandpa and Yuanbao's grandma?

70
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,200
You sure have a wild imagination.

71
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,410
I think it's highly likely.

72
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,800
I think if we just give them a little push,

73
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,800
and help them out.

74
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:15,500
Is it appropriate?

75
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,240
I don't know how your grandma

76
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,720
has been doing all these years.

77
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,180
But I think it's been tough

78
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,640
for my grandpa alone.

79
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:23,280
I hope after I go to college,

80
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:25,520
he can find a companion to spend the rest of his life with.

81
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:27,050
When you guys go to college,

82
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,520
you wouldn't want Yuanbao's grandma

83
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,250
to be home alone either, right?

84
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:32,420
How about we talk to Yuanbao about it?

85
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,760
Let's not tell Yuanbao for now.

86
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:38,240
Because she still seems to have some prejudice against you.

87
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,240
Besides,

88
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,040
we don't even know

89
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:43,240
our grandparents' true thoughts, do we?

90
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,440
My grandpa is a rare, good man.

91
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:48,159
You won't find another one like him.

92
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,800
Our grandma raised Yuanbao and me.

93
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:53,280
She is known as the queen of virtue.

94
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,600
So many old men are lining up to woo her.

95
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,000
She has high standards.

96
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,159
She wouldn't settle for just anyone.

97
00:06:58,159 --> 00:07:00,200
My grandpa is quite a gentleman too.

98
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,490
He wouldn't just like anybody.

99
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,400
My grandma's cooking smells amazing,

100
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,920
and she's great at everything inside and outside the house.

101
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,600
My grandpa's skills aren't bad either.

102
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,240
He dances square dancing so well

103
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:11,480
that the old ladies in the team fight to be his partner.

104
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,280
When my grandma was young,

105
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:13,520
she almost became a singer.

106
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:15,040
Even now, her voice is as good as Li Guyi's.

107
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,520
Well, my grandpa...

108
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:17,320
My grandma...

109
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,020
How about this?

110
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,610
I'll think about it.

111
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,440
Okay, but hurry up.

112
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,300
Since you are in Zhicheng now,

113
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:31,860
I'll cover you from now on.

114
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,409
Alright, I'll count on you.

115
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:38,640
Where did you get this dirt from?

116
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,640
So that's how it is.

117
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:49,120
I'm sorry.

118
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:51,000
I misunderstood you.

119
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:54,260
I'm sorry. I apologize to both of you.

120
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,840
Gong Yu.

121
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,600
I'm sorry.

122
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,960
What a mess.

123
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,360
You guys were so secretive

124
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,720
and kept me in the dark.

125
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:09,360
Good thing the date didn't happen.

126
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:10,760
Wait.

127
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,640
Why shouldn't they

128
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:13,000
give dating a try?

129
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,960
You planned this for days

130
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,170
without telling me.

131
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,840
She's my actual grandma.

132
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,240
What do you mean?

133
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,240
What do you mean she's your actual grandma?

134
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:21,840
Isn't she

135
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,580
the same as my actual grandma?

136
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:25,800
Besides, nothing's set in stone yet.

137
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,200
If you knew earlier,

138
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,600
it would've been ruined.

139
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,280
It's not too late now.

140
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,600
Good thing it's ruined.

141
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,039
For something so important,

142
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:35,000
how could you decide so easily?

143
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:38,000
Besides, what kind of person he is,

144
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,360
we still don't know.

145
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:43,929
What are you talking about?

146
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:44,800
Gong Yu.

147
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:45,920
Sorry about that.

148
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:46,960
She didn't mean it.

149
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,480
She doesn't know you well yet.

150
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,240
It's fine.

151
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:52,800
It's just that Grandpa and Grandma were quite embarrassed just now.

152
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,660
A perfectly good date was ruined.

153
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,540
Since you know about this,

154
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:04,040
you should think it over carefully.

155
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,880
We'll see.

156
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:09,240
Gong Yu, take Ruirui home later.

157
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,880
What? Take Ruirui home?

158
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:13,840
No.

159
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:14,720
You two.

160
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,250
Let's go.

161
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:18,240
Grandma is waiting for us to go home for dinner. Hurry up.

162
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:18,800
You two.

163
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,400
Those two.

164
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,640
Don't pull me.

165
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,800
Let's go. I'll take you home.

166
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,600
Mu Qingjun,

167
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,120
you're really getting more and more opinionated.

168
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,960
My friends,

169
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,170
my grandmother,

170
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:02,040
you can make decisions about them

171
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,320
without my permission.

172
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,600
Gong Yu is no good.

173
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,850
His grandfather is even worse.

174
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,120
Yuanbao.

175
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,040
Yuanbao, listen to me, Yuanbao.

176
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,360
Gong Yu is really a very good person.

177
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,200
Trust me.

178
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,560
Lately,

179
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:36,160
I've been intentionally distancing myself from you.

180
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,360
I apologize for that.

181
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:41,120
Actually, I'm really not good at making friends,

182
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:42,960
especially with girls.

183
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,800
If I said anything that hurt you,

184
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:47,800
I'm sorry.

185
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,400
Why are you

186
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,920
telling me all this so suddenly?

187
00:10:57,920 --> 00:11:00,720
Actually, I'm not very good at expressing myself,

188
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:03,600
whether it's with friends or classmates.

189
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,970
So I haven't made any good friends.

190
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,880
As for Mu Qingjun,

191
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,760
we became friends after a fight.

192
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:13,410
And I happened to meet your grandparents.

193
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,140
Do you have any dreams?

194
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:20,840
My parents are both doctors.

195
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,040
So,

196
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,680
they hope

197
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,420
I can be a doctor in the future.

198
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,700
What about you?

199
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,320
I

200
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,960
want to be someone like Liu Xiang.

201
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:33,880
To become an Olympic champion

202
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:35,540
and win glory for the country.

203
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:38,200
Your dream is so great.

204
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,760
You can definitely do it.

205
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,480
You see, we both have our own dreams.

206
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:48,640
So,

207
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:52,660
I really don't want to affect you.

208
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:55,520
And,

209
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,980
I'm really not good at being friends with girls.

210
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,920
I understand what you mean.

211
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:14,840
From now on,

212
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:20,480
I won't force you to be friends with me anymore.

213
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:25,200
Aren't we already friends?

214
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,600
Nice to meet you.

215
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,400
Nice to meet you too.

216
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:39,880
Let's go.

217
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:50,120
If Gong Yu's grandpa and my grandma get together,

218
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:54,200
wouldn't Gong Yu become my older brother?

219
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,760
If years later,

220
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,000
Ruirui and Gong Yu get together,

221
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:02,960
wouldn't Ruirui become my sister-in-law?

222
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,600
Oh, my God!

223
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,640
Gong Yu even hits girls.

224
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,760
No, no, no.

225
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,640
No, no.

226
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:11,920
I absolutely won't allow it.

227
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:13,520
I can't let them be together.

228
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,020
What am I thinking?

229
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,320
Study hard. Study hard.

230
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:20,400
It didn't happen. It didn't happen.

231
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:21,800
Study hard. Study hard.

232
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:49,730
Leaving it at the door all night, aren't you afraid of attracting mice?

233
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:53,000
Honestly, who apologizes like this?

234
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:56,200
Don't think a piece of cake

235
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,920
can buy me off.

236
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:39,800
Every falling baby's breath

237
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:41,840
is like the apple falling

238
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:43,720
on Newton's head.

239
00:14:44,520 --> 00:14:45,720
Thump, thump.

240
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:47,740
Landing right on my heart,

241
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:49,960
making my heart flutter.

242
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,720
So much so that ever since then,

243
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:54,610
whenever I see this flower,

244
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:56,640
I feel inexplicably excited.

245
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,360
This silly blockhead

246
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:00,920
always brings me joy and sorrow.

247
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:08,520
Brother,

248
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:09,080
Yuanbao,

249
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,280
