250
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:12,280
Look.

251
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:16,200
Someone posted Yuanbao's photo on the forum.

252
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:47,600
Who did this?

253
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,560
It's you again, isn't it?

254
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:55,040
What are you doing?

255
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,680
It wasn't me.

256
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,120
Don't falsely accuse me.

257
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:01,520
Mu Qingyun.

258
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:20,840
I believe everyone saw it on the forum.

259
00:16:22,680 --> 00:16:24,880
Yes, that was me.

260
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:36,940
Thanks to the anonymous kind person for helping me promote it.

261
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:40,520
From now on, if you have empty water bottles,

262
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:42,060
you can give them to me.

263
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:45,600
It really saves me a lot of effort.

264
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:48,460
I don't have to look for them everywhere.

265
