Keep it up, Yuanbao.

278
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:06,000
Thank you, everyone.

279
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,680
Who is in charge of the sophomore forum?

280
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:29,320
Yes, yes, it's me.

281
00:18:29,560 --> 00:18:32,120
Go delete the post about Xiong Yuanbao right now.

282
00:18:32,120 --> 00:18:32,920
